songs.title: Greenlight
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: Calum & Michael]
It started with a picture, those messages you sent to me
You’re like the perfect mixture of Megan Fox and Katy P
It’s such a sick obsession and now you've got the best of me
I've got the worst intentions, so call me over set me free

[Pre-Chorus: Michael]
I can give you what you want

[Chorus: All]
It’s taking me over
I don’t wanna play this game no more
All you gotta do is tell me right now
You want me right now, come on
Give me the green light
We could have all night
If you just say the words
Tell me it’s alright, give me the green light

[Verse 2: Luke]
You got me where you want me
I'm hanging on your every word
It’s such a twisted story
How you got me, now you got me

[Pre-Chorus: Luke]
So let me give you what you need

[Chorus: All]
It’s taking me over
I don’t wanna play this game no more
All you gotta do is tell me right now
You want me right now, come on
Give me the green light
We could have all night
If you just say the words
Tell me it’s alright, give me the green light

[Bridge: Calum]
So let me give you what you need

[Chorus: All & Calum]
It’s taking me over
I don’t wanna play this game no more
All you gotta do is tell me right now
You want me right now, come on
Give me the green light, we could have all night
If you just say the words, tell me it’s alright, give me the green light
